		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The IDRC site provides a wealth of information on the subject of Adaptive Technology. We have an extensive collection of research papers published by ATRC and IDRC staff available in full-text. We have also created a number of tutorials to aid in the installation and use of various common adaptive software packages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A related site, &lt;a href=&quot;http://snow.idrc.ocad.ca&quot;&gt;SNOW (Special Needs Opportunity Window)&lt;/a&gt;, is also an excellent resource for online information.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;The IDRC site provides a wealth of information on the subject of Adaptive Technology. We have an extensive collection of research papers published by ATRC and IDRC staff available in full-text. We have also created a number of tutorials to aid in the installation and use of various common adaptive software packages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A related site, &lt;a href=&quot;http://snow.idrc.ocad.ca&quot;&gt;SNOW (Special Needs Opportunity Window)&lt;/a&gt;, is also an excellent resource for online information.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
